data.description:
I am pleased to present this beautiful duplex in the Westpark neighborhood of Cleveland. Close to airport, highways, Kamm's corner and Fairview hospital. This home has so much potential! A little improvement will go a very long way with this property. Both units on 1st floor and 2nd floor are very identical but the third-floor finished area with full bathroom offers more living space. Downstairs unit is currently occupied till feb 2024.the upstairs unit is ready to be owner occupied or rent it out for extra income potential. Both units have a wonderful view of the street.
call for the private showing!
